data.description: Welcome to your beautifully remodeled home in an ideal location! This house has seen extensive upgrades, and the result is a perfect blend of modern convenience and classic charm.    The front landscape is adorned with fragrant lavender, aromatic rosemary, and vibrant yellow roses, creating a picturesque entryway that welcomes you home.    The exterior boasts a fresh coat of exterior paint, creating an inviting and well-maintained appearance. As you step into the backyard, you'll discover a peaceful oasis with a retaining wall and raised garden beds, perfect for those with a green thumb. A spacious cement back patio offers a great space for outdoor gatherings and relaxation.    Inside, a comprehensive remodel was completed just three years ago, including new windows, doors, blinds, interior paint, and new carpeting. The result is a fresh, bright, and welcoming interior.    You'll enjoy the convenience of a smart thermostat, allowing you to control the climate with ease and energy efficiency. In the kitchen, new quartz counters and bright cabinets provide ample workspace and storage, complemented by updated appliances that make meal preparation a pleasure.    The downstairs bathroom has been elegantly remodeled, and the upstairs bath features a new vanity with a beautiful quartz counter, bringing a touch of luxury to your daily routine.    For those who work or study from home, a new built-in desk and organizer in the guest bedroom make productivity a breeze.    The recent HVAC service ensures your comfort throughout the year, regardless of the season.    This home's location is unbeatable, situated in close proximity to Chico's new Rotary Centennial Park, offering a wealth of recreational opportunities and green space right at your doorstep.    Don't miss this opportunity to own a beautifully remodeled home in a prime location. Schedule a tour today and experience the perfect blend of modern living and classic charm.
